  "BCM AFTER SALES PAIRING": {
   "width": 10140,
   "height": 9900,
   "color": "rgb(128,0,128)",
   "labels": [
    {
     "text": "Protected Pairing : HFM pairing in After Sales ",
     "color": "rgb(232,191,224)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,128)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 105,
      "top": 45,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 9735
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Procedure : ",
     "color": "rgb(216,175,228)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 120,
      "top": 1440,
      "height": 3720,
      "width": 9735
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 8.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "1) You need first to connect to the application \"Pairing using DDT2000\" : https://gco.intra.renault.fr:14053/gco/ctrl/login and enter your IPN and Password. Then come back to this screen.",
     "color": "rgb(216,175,228)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 1680,
      "height": 405,
      "width": 7905
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "2) Press the button \"Request Server HFM pairing\"",
     "color": "rgb(216,175,228)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 2160,
      "height": 255,
      "width": 9600
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "3) Select the \"Input Data Server\" (19 bytes) and copy it in the application \"Pairing using DDT2000\".  ",
     "color": "rgb(216,175,228)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 2520,
      "height": 465,
      "width": 9480
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "4) Complete the frames in the application and press the button \"Calcul\".Get the \"Server answer\" (16 bytes) and copy it in this screen. Then press the button \"Transmit Server Answer\" ",
     "color": "rgb(216,175,228)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 3000,
      "height": 1260,
      "width": 9600
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "5) If the HFM is SA unlocked for HFM pairing then insert the customer ID belonging to the vehicle in the reader or switch Ignition Power Supply ON and press the button \"HFM pairing\" to pair the blank BCM. ",
     "color": "rgb(216,175,228)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 240,
      "top": 4320,
      "height": 720,
      "width": 9480
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 7.0,
      "bold": "0",
