     }
    },
    {
     "text": "2) Check that the ECM is blank (try to start the vehicle) and read the ECM information \" VSC_UCH voit INJECTION vierge ou cod\u00e9e\"",
     "color": "rgb(239,239,239)",
     "alignment": "0",
